# Netlify _redirects — pretty URLs.
# https://docs.netlify.com/routing/redirects/
#
# Netlify's "Pretty URLs" feature is on by default for deploys, but we
# add explicit 200-rewrites for the canonical short paths the
# security.txt + Responsible Disclosure documents reference. Explicit
# rules guard against a future Netlify config change that flips Pretty
# URLs off.

/security        /security.html         200
/status          /status.html           200
/docs            /docs.html             200
/cctp-explainer  /cctp-explainer.html   200
